<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Congratulations! — TektonX</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
    .header { background: #0f172a; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #f8fafc; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .header span { color: #38bdf8; }
    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #6366f1); padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .hero .emoji { font-size: 48px; }
    .hero h2 { color: #ffffff; margin: 12px 0 0; font-size: 22px; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body p { color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; margin: 12px 0; }
    .track-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px; background: #ede9fe; color: #4c1d95; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin: 8px 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; margin: 24px 0 8px; padding: 12px 28px; background: #0ea5e9; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 40px; background: #f8fafc; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Tekton<span>X</span></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="emoji">🎉</div>
      <h2>Program Complete!</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Congratulations, <strong>{{name}}</strong>!</p>
      <p>You've completed the TektonX mentorship program.</p>
      <span class="track-badge">{{track}} Track</span>
      <p>This is a huge achievement and a testament to your dedication and hard work. Your certificate of completion is ready to download from your dashboard.</p>
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">View My Certificate</a>
      <p>We're proud of how far you've come. Stay connected with the TektonX community — you're now part of our alumni network.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} TektonX Labs. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
